title: Fed Decision, China Imports, Middle East

description:
Guests: Ken Cuccinelli, acting Homeland Security Deputy Secretary, Robert Shapiro, Chairman of Sonecon, Matt Brooks, Republican strategist and Executive Director of the Republican Jewish Coalition, Joel Rubin, Democratic strategist and former Deputy Assistant Secretary for Legislative Affairs at the State Department, and Congressman David Schweikert, a Republican representing Arizona's 6th district.
